creator: Tzutalin
descriptionHtml:
DriveRecorder is a free and car dash camera app which can record the video when driving, and it will give you an extra pair of eyes when driving. In the future, we will keep adding more features if this app really helps you, therefore, please rate this app to let us know if this app is helpful to you.

Current major features:
- Support recording in the background
- Support recording repeatedly
- Auto recording once you launch the app
- Support different video resolutions and file size
- Support specifying the video storage size
- Support sharing the video to your cloud drive
- Support records driving trajectory
- Support navigation based on video location

If you have any problems or issues to use this app, please go to the bug report page.
https://github.com/tzutalin/DriveRecorder

Note: We highly recommended that your OS of Android should be 4.0 or higher.

title: Drive Recorder

creator: Tzutalin
descriptionHtml:
Turn your Android Smartphone into a car dash camera today!

Drive Recorder is a free dash cam app which helps you continuously capture what is happening on the road while you are driving.

The app automatically documents everything, but you can easily choose what to keep or edit videos within the app's amazing editing function.

Drive Recorder is constantly being upgraded, and we are committed to providing you with the best user experience possible.


Current major features:
- Support multiple languages
- Support recording repeatedly
- Auto recording once you launch the app
- Support different video resolutions and file sizes
- User-defined video storage size
- Back up recorded videos to the cloud like YouTube, Drive, etc
- Support recording the driving trajectory and speed, and visualize the trajectory on Map
- Support navigating to the last location in the video
- Built-in video editing function
- Remind a driver when driving too fast
descriptionShort: A car dash camera will give you an extra pair of eyes when driving

* Remove unnecessary permission
